# PortfolioSim - Trading Strategy Backtesting Framework
A Python-based platform for backtesting trading strategies, analyzing portfolio performance, and simulating investment scenarios with multi-asset support.

## âœ¨ Key Features

- ğŸ“ˆ **Multi-Asset Portfolio Management** - Track stocks, cash positions, and transactions
- ğŸ¤– **Strategy Backtesting** - Test moving average, seasonal, and custom strategies
- ğŸ“‰ **Risk Analysis** - Value-at-Risk (VaR) and basic risk metrics
- ğŸ“Š **Performance Visualization** - Visualize charts for returns and allocations
- âš¡ **YFinance Integration** - Automatic S&P 500 data downloading
- ğŸ¤  **Summary & Benchmarks** - Get summary of strategy and compare with buy-hold benchmark

## ğŸ“Š Core Functionality
Component	                Description	                            Status
Portfolio Tracking	   Holdings, cash balance, transactions	        âœ… Stable
